{"word":"G4291 - προΐστημι - proḯstēmi - pro-is'-tay-mee - Maintain","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προΐστημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">proḯstēmi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro-is'-tay-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Maintain</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முதலாளியாயிரு, நடத்து, விசாரணைசெய்"},{"paragraph":"1. to set place before; to set over"},{"paragraph":"2. to be over, to superintend preside over"},{"paragraph":"3. to be a protector or guardian; to give aid"},{"paragraph":"4. to care for, give attention to"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2476 - ἵστημι - hístēmi - his'-tay-mee/2476\">G2476</a>; to <i>stand before</i>, that is, (in rank) to <i>preside</i>, or (by implication) to <i>practise:</i> - maintain, be over, rule.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4291/4291\">G4291</a>, <a href=\"#/G547/547\">G547</a>"}]}